	screentext STARTALPHANUM 18 55 29500 0 0 3305 0 0 16 0 5 8 TX_GP 1 0 0 0 xdim ydim
	screentext STARTALPHANUM 18 65 29500 0 0 3306 0 0 16 0 5 8 TX_GP 1 0 0 0 xdim ydim
	screentext STARTALPHANUM 18 70 29500 0 0 3307 0 0 16 0 5 8 TX_GP 1 0 0 0 xdim ydim
	screentext STARTALPHANUM 18 80 29500 0 0 3308 0 0 16 0 5 8 TX_GP 1 0 0 0 xdim ydim
